items.title: Awesome Pascal
items.content_text:
### Game dev

*   [TurboRaylib (⭐39)](https://github.com/turborium/TurboRaylib). `[Delphi]` `[FPC]` TurboRaylib is a cool and clean [raylib](https://www.raylib.com/) bindings for Object Pascal. Support Windows, Linux, OSX. TurboRaylib have many examples that work in Delphi and Lazarus.
